      "raw_text": "The tunnel was one of the chief\npower developments figured on by\nthe Washington Water Power cons-\npany two years ago when 1t author\nICED the issuance OF 315,000.000 In\nbonds for gigantic extensions OF\nvarious kinds.\n\n\nSince then the Post Falls dam\nhas been completed. the dam at\nLittle Falls nearly so, immense\nbuildings have been erected and the\ntracks of the company's street rail-\nway system In Spokane practically\nrebuilt and scores of new cars put\non the city lines.\n\n\nThe last and greatest of all Ia\nthe immense tunnel proposition on\nwhich work was begun this week."
